# 📊 Time Series Analysis: Industrial Gas Production & Garden Equipment Sales

## 📖 Overview

This project was carried out as part of the **Time Series Analysis** course at **ESEN (École Supérieure d'Économie Numérique)**.

The objective is to perform a complete statistical and forecasting analysis of two monthly time series obtained from official U.S. economic databases.

### Datasets

#### 🔥 Industrial Production: Electric and Gas Utilities

* Source: Federal Reserve Economic Data (FRED)
* Series ID: IPG2211A2N
* Period: January 1990 – March 2024
* Observations: 411

#### 🌿 Retail Sales: Building Materials & Garden Equipment

* Source: U.S. Census Bureau
* NAICS Code: 444
* Period: January 1992 – December 2024
* Observations: 387

---

## 🎯 Objectives

* Explore and visualize temporal patterns
* Identify trend and seasonality components
* Test stationarity using statistical methods
* Build forecasting models using ARIMA methodology
* Evaluate model performance and residual diagnostics
* Generate 24-month forecasts with confidence intervals

---

